
@host = http://localhost:3000

### --- PRODUCTS ------------------------------------------------------------

### GET products (lista)
GET {{host}}/api/products

### POST product (201 Created + Location)
POST {{host}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zeszyt A4",
  "price": 7.50
}

### PATCH product (zmiana ceny)
# Uzupełnij {id} po wcześniejszym GET
PATCH {{host}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 8.00
}

### DELETE product (204)
# Uzupełnij {id} właściwym produktem
DELETE {{host}}/api/products/999

### --- CART (per-session via cookie) ---------------------------------------

### GET cart (zawartość + total)
GET {{host}}/api/cart

### ADD to cart (product_id, qty)
POST {{host}}/api/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": 1,
  "qty": 2
}

### UPDATE cart item qty
PATCH {{host}}/api/cart/item
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": 1,
  "qty": 5
}

### REMOVE cart item
DELETE {{host}}/api/cart/item/1

### --- CHECKOUT ------------------------------------------------------------

### POST checkout (201 -> {order_id,total}; czyści koszyk)
POST {{host}}/api/checkout

### (Opcjonalnie) sprawdź koszyk po checkout (powinien być pusty)
GET {{host}}/api/cart

